    <summary type="text/plain">uploads are now stored in a new location, with files named according to their database id. we seem to have enough disk space to stop expiring files and with that in mind files are stored in a directory hierarchy according...</summary>
    <author>
      <name>ray</name>
      <url>http://themaxx.com</url>
      <email>geek@themaxx.com</email>
    </author>
    
    <content type="text/html" mode="escaped" xml:lang="en" xml:base="http://themaxx.com/">
      <![CDATA[<p>uploads are now stored in a new location, with files named according to their database id. we seem to have enough disk space to stop expiring files and with that in mind files are stored in a directory hierarchy according to date, e.g. "uploads/2007/02/17/image/188999.jpg".</p>

<p>thumbnails generation is now invoked by the upload processing script instead of a periodic cron task. still need to update the thumbnails page to account for this, so the thumbnails now exist in both the new and old locations.</p>]]>
      
    </content>
